    "description": "The Way of Death is a souls-like game set in a world inspired by feudal Japan from the Edo period. Take the challenge in the arcade sword combat system prepared for a group fight in a top-down perspective. Defeat opponents and bosses, explore full of secrets surroundings, and overcome death as you battle in the Afterlife.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/14e73de4769755840038bdc9e2c52377.poster.avif?t=1751980185\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/14e73de4769755840038bdc9e2c52377.webm?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/14e73de4769755840038bdc9e2c52377.mp4?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >MAIN FEATURES</h2><strong>SKILFUL COMBAT SYSTEM</strong><br>Your sword is the most helpful tool to survive. Learn how to use it and become a better swordsman. You will be surrounded by dangerous monsters many times. The proper tactic is required to beat them. Also, thrilling duels on swords await you. Parry all the hits and beat the enemy.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/fdc5ccc2a17d509e248a5b8c3b0998f6.poster.avif?t=1751980185\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/fdc5ccc2a17d509e248a5b8c3b0998f6.webm?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/fdc5ccc2a17d509e248a5b8c3b0998f6.mp4?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>DEATH IS THE CONTINUATION</strong><br>Death is an inherent element of the game. After death, fight your way back to life with the new, unique Afterlife mechanic.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/a28ac8ad2edad33282ef2ad09901bd27.poster.avif?t=1751980185\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/a28ac8ad2edad33282ef2ad09901bd27.webm?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/a28ac8ad2edad33282ef2ad09901bd27.mp4?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>MYSTERIOUS WORLD</strong><br>Walk across mysterious terrain and reveal its secrets. Perhaps, the reality is not as simple as it seems. Do not be afraid to get off the main path; maybe you will find something unexpected.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/c6f62837af053a5589d526207d2299c9.poster.avif?t=1751980185\" width=600 height=228 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/c6f62837af053a5589d526207d2299c9.webm?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2346000/extras/c6f62837af053a5589d526207d2299c9.mp4?t=1751980185\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
